## Auto Memory

This project uses Claude's auto-memory system. Save memories when you learn:
- User preferences or workflow patterns
- Project decisions and their rationale
- External references (Linear, Slack, Notion, etc.)
- Feedback on your approach that should persist

Prune memories that are:
- Outdated by newer decisions
- Duplicated by what's in the code or git history
- No longer relevant to the current project state

